    "description": {
      "value": "<p><em><strong>Ballistic Approach:</strong> 3rd and 9th level</em></p>\n<p>While raging, you gain the following benefits:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>When you roll a 1 or 2 on a damage die for an attack made with a blaster weapon, you can reroll the die and must use the new roll, even if the new roll is a 1 or a 2.</li>\n<li>You add your rage damage to damage rolls from ranged weapon attacks using Strength. </li>\n<li>At 9th level, when a creature rolls a 1 on a saving throw against your burst or rapid property, you can add your Brutal Critical dice to the damage.</li></ul>",
